Watch on youtube: https://youtu.be/QBZOp1oNi34 Tags: 3dprint , creality , strength test , material test , This is the second part of my Creality filament review, in this part you can see mechanical tests of CR-PLA, CR-SILK, CR-PETG, CR-TPU, CR-ABS and CR-Carbon (enhanced version, Nylon carbon fiber). PLA, PETG and ABS filaments I bought myself. TPU, SILK and Carbon filaments are sent to me by Creality.
